						               													<description>The Battle of Brovary was a clash during the Kyiv offensive of the 2022 Russian invasion of Ukraine for control of the suburb of Brovary, to the east of the capital city of Ukraine, Kyiv. Russian forces advanced west from southern Chernihiv Oblast and were engaged by Ukrainian forces. Control of the suburb was contested until Russian forces withdrew on 2 April 2022.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Brovary 2022 is a company scale game about the first part of the battle, covering three days long Russian assault on Brovary, led by the Russian 90th Guards Tank Division. It is a part of the Battles of XXI Century (B-XXI) system, highly detailed company scale system dedicated for the modern combat.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game was published in the 46 issue of the Tactics and Strategy magazine, in both Polish and English languages. A copy of any boxed game of B-XXI system is required.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
